    "descriptionHtml": "<p>Starting at 2nd level, your speed increases by 10 feet while you are not wearing armor or wielding a shield. This bonus increases when you reach certain monk levels, as shown in the Monk table.</p>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"indent\">At 9th level, you gain the ability to move along vertical surfaces and across liquids on your turn without falling during the move.</p>"
