    "setters": [],
    "descriptionHtml": "<p>You focus your training on the grim art of death. Those who adhere to this archetype are diverse: hired killers, spies, bounty hunters, and even specially anointed priests trained to exterminate the enemies of their deity. Stealth, poison, and disguise help you eliminate your foes with deadly efficiency.</p>\n\t\t\t<div element=\"ID_WOTC_PHB_ARCHETYPE_FEATURE_BONUSPROFICIENCIES\" />\n\t\t\t<div element=\"ID_WOTC_PHB_ARCHETYPE_FEATURE_ASSASSINATE\" />\n\t\t\t<div element=\"ID_WOTC_PHB_ARCHETYPE_FEATURE_INFILTRATIONEXPERTISE\" />\n\t\t\t<div element=\"ID_WOTC_PHB_ARCHETYPE_FEATURE_IMPOSTER\" />\n\t\t\t<div element=\"ID_WOTC_PHB_ARCHETYPE_FEATURE_DEATHSTRIKE\" />"
