    "descriptionHtml": "<p>Some rogues enhance their fine-honed skills of stealth and agility with magic, learning tricks of enchantment and illusion. These rogues include pickpockets and burglars, but also pranksters, mischief-makers, and a significant number of adventurers.</p>\n\t\t\t<div element=\"ID_WOTC_PHB_ARCHETYPE_FEATURE_ARCANE_TRICKSTER_SPELLCASTING\" />\n\t\t\t<div element=\"ID_WOTC_PHB_ARCHETYPE_FEATURE_ARCANE_TRICKSTER_MAGE_HAND_LEGERDEMAIN\" />\n\t\t\t<div element=\"ID_WOTC_PHB_ARCHETYPE_FEATURE_ARCANE_TRICKSTER_MAGICAL_AMBUSH\" />\n\t\t\t<div element=\"ID_WOTC_PHB_ARCHETYPE_FEATURE_ARCANE_TRICKSTER_VERSATILE_TRICKSTER\" />\n\t\t\t<div element=\"ID_WOTC_PHB_ARCHETYPE_FEATURE_ARCANE_TRICKSTER_SPELL_THIEF\" />"
