    "description": "The Archfey lets you choose from an expanded list of spells when you learn a warlock spell. The following spells are added to the warlock spell list for you.  \t\t\t ARCHFEY EXPANDED SPELLS  \t\t\t  \t\t\t\t  \t\t\t\t\t  Spell Level  Spells   \t\t\t\t  \t\t\t\t  1st   faerie fire, sleep    \t\t\t\t  2nd   calm emotions, phantasmal force    \t\t\t\t  3rd   blink, plant growth    \t\t\t\t  4th   dominate beast, greater invisibility    \t\t\t\t  5th   dominate person, seeming",
    "rules": [],
    "setters": [],
    "descriptionHtml": "<p>The Archfey lets you choose from an expanded list of spells when you learn a warlock spell. The following spells are added to the warlock spell list for you.</p>\n\t\t\t<h5 class=\"caption\">ARCHFEY EXPANDED SPELLS</h5>\n\t\t\t<table>\n\t\t\t\t<thead>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr><td>Spell Level</td><td>Spells</td></tr>\n\t\t\t\t</thead>\n\t\t\t\t<tr><td>1st</td><td><em>faerie fire, sleep</em></td></tr>\n\t\t\t\t<tr><td>2nd</td><td><em>calm emotions, phantasmal force</em></td></tr>\n\t\t\t\t<tr><td>3rd</td><td><em>blink, plant growth</em></td></tr>\n\t\t\t\t<tr><td>4th</td><td><em>dominate beast, greater invisibility</em></td></tr>\n\t\t\t\t<tr><td>5th</td><td><em>dominate person, seeming</em></td></tr>\n\t\t\t</table>",
