    "setters": [],
    "descriptionHtml": "<p>The counsel of a diviner is sought by royalty and commoners alike, for all seek a clearer understanding of the past, present, and future. As a diviner, you strive to part the veils of space, time, and consciousness so that you can see clearly. You work to master spells of discernment, remote viewing, supernatural knowledge, and foresight.</p>\n\t\t\t<div element=\"ID_WOTC_PHB_ARCHETYPE_FEATURE_WIZARD_DIVINATION_DIVINATION_SAVANT\" />\n\t\t\t<div element=\"ID_WOTC_PHB_ARCHETYPE_FEATURE_WIZARD_DIVINATION_PORTENT\" />\n\t\t\t<div element=\"ID_WOTC_PHB_ARCHETYPE_FEATURE_WIZARD_DIVINATION_EXPERT_DIVINATION\" />\n\t\t\t<div element=\"ID_WOTC_PHB_ARCHETYPE_FEATURE_WIZARD_DIVINATION_THE_THIRD_EYE\" />\n\t\t\t<div element=\"ID_WOTC_PHB_ARCHETYPE_FEATURE_WIZARD_DIVINATION_GREATER_PORTENT\" />"
